title: FSI - Korean Volume I and II (complete)
description:
This complete course is intended to give someone basic proficiency with the Korean language.  It is a digitization of the course used by the United States Foreign Service Institute to train diplomats and other federal agents in the language skills they would need.

The pdf files contain the translations corresponding to each lesson.  The mp3 files contain almost no English, but are there to aid in understanding the pronunciation of words in the corresponding pdf files.
